==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unerring
<hw>Un*err"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Committing no
mistake; incapable or error or failure certain; sure; unfailing; <as>as,
the <ex>unerring</ex> wisdom of God</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Hissing in air the <qex>unerring</qex> weapon flew.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unerringly</ent>⟦br⟧
